{ 3. Bb5+ has helped black develop  (trades the bishops but develops black's queen)  but Bc8 was black's good bishop. Black can play Nc6 with Nf6 and g6 Bg7  (e6 Be7 is an alternative, which one is used depends on what white plays)  and O-O with easy play. }
