{ Black is better developed and white's d-pawn is isolated. Black can develop quickly with ...♗f5/♗g4 with ...e6 ...♗e7 and ...O-O.   7...Bg4!?  is an interesting gambit for the aggressive player.  8.dxe7  Bxe7  Black has a huge lead in development. }
