{ Black wins a pawn and prepares to trade queens with Qc6 or Qc4. He can soon finish his development with a good position. Here is a sample continuation: }
12. Nc3 Qc4 13. Qg5 Nd5 14. Nge2 Nxc3
{ Black is ahead a pawn, his king is safe in the center. He can finish his development with Nc6 g6 and Bg7, and has the option of Kd7 if needed. }
