3... Nf6
{ Accepting the gambit is playable, but dangerous. White gets a lot of dangerous compensation. This transposes into the Alapin   2.c3  sicilian  or white gets an inferior version of black taking on c3 right away. }
4. e5 Nd5 { Transposing into 2.c3. } *

